      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EIFFEL FROM HEAVEN (8) ran fifth last start at Tamworth over 1609m, beaten 12 metres. Should enjoy a nice smother from this draw and will be looking for a split at some stage. Finds a nice race and will be a major force. ANTETOKOUNMPO (7) finished third at Newcastle two runs ago before finishing seventh at his latest appearance over 1609m at Tamworth, beaten 22 metres. Drawn to enjoy a cosy run but might need things to go his way at some stage. Meets a similar line up and he can figure in the finish. WHISKEY ROYALE (4) is worth plenty of thought off a last-start win by 9 metres at Tamworth over 1609m. KATASTROPHEE (5) is in the mix following a respectable third at her most recent appearance over 1609m at Tamworth.",
